(Future ;-) FIDOGATE debug() level standard:


0	* no debug messages

1	* log() messages
	* interactive messages

2	* packet grade, type, flavor, node

3	* packet header
	* matching routing/packing commands

4	* detailed packet processing
	* detailed processing of packet and archive files
	* commands executed
	* MSGID history expire parameters
	* areas.bbs file processing

5	* messages processed (interesting information)

6	* message header

7	* detailed message processing
	* MSGID records in history
	* lock files

8	* configuration
	  - standard config stuff
	  - optional config statements in various programs	  

9	* internal processing

14	* config files being read

15	* stuff being read from config files (parsed)

16	* lines read from config files
